Warrior 12-15 Barrens
01) Run to Far Watch Post and behind the watchtower, turn in your warrior quest "Veteran Uzzek [QT1505-]" (61,21), accept "Path of Defense [QA1498-]".
02) Cross the bridge east to Durotar, run north into the canyon Thunder Ridge (entrance at 39,31 in Durotar) and do "Path of Defense [QC1498-]": kill/loot the lizards in this area.
03) Go SE to Razor Hill and at the west entrance, accept "Conscript of the Horde [QA840-]" (51,43).
04) Cross the bridge back to The Barrens, go to Far Watch Post and turn in "Conscript of the Horde [QT840-]", accept "Crossroads Conscription [QA842-]".  Behind the watchtower, turn in "Path of Defense [QT1498-]" (61,21), accept "Thun'grim Firegaze [QA1502-]".
05) Next to the Razormane camp, go to the path that leads up the mountain (starts at 54.28).  Run up the mountain crest..
06) Run up the mountain to Thun'grim Firegaze (57,30) and turn in "Thun'grim Firegaze [QT1502-]", accept "Forged Steel [QA1503-]".
07) Run down the mountain the same way you came up and go to (55,27) at the Razormane camp, then do "Forged Steel [QC1503-]": loot the Stolen Iron Chest that is in front of the broken down wagon.
08) In the immediate area, do "Disrupt the Attacks [QC871-]": kill the needed Razormane gnolls (all around 54.27).  ALSO:  Back in the Razormane camp is a barrel called Chen's Empty Keg (56.27), loot it and accept the quest [QA819-] from the item received.
09) Run up the mountain to Thun'grim Firegaze again (57,30, numbers 5-6 on map) and turn in "Forged Steel [QT1503-]".
10) Go back to XRs and turn in "Crossroads Conscription [QT842-]" and (if it's complete) "Plainstrider Menace [QT844-]" (from Sergra Darkthorn 52.31), accept "The Zhevra [QA845-]".
11) At the orc standing at the bottom of the watch tower, turn in "Disrupt the Attacks [QT871-]" (52.30), accept "The Disruption Ends [QA872-]".  Make sure you are repaired/resupplied.
